#

Quick and Easy Borscht

40 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

soupquickhealthy

Description

A vibrant beet soup that's both hearty and refreshing, perfect for any time of the year.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrot: 1 large, grated
  • potato: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • dill: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • sour cream: for serving
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
